18.907" end="3:19.269">sharp</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">棱角愈发锋利</span></p><p begin="3:19.438" end="3:25.549" itunes:key="L56" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:19.438" end="3:19.627">And</span> <span begin="3:19.627" end="3:19.926">now</span> <span begin="3:19.926" end="3:20.255">you</span> <span begin="3:20.255" end="3:20.566">know</span> <span begin="3:20.566" end="3:21.589">exactly</span> <span begin="3:21.589" end="3:21.928">who</span> <span begin="3:21.928" end="3:22.146">your</span> <span begin="3:22.146" end="3:22.939">friends</span> <span begin="3:22.939" end="3:24.341">are</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">如今你终于看清 谁才是真朋友</span><span ttm:role="x-bg" begin="3:23.407" end="3:25.549"><span begin="3:23.407" end="3:23.885">(You</span> <span begin="3:23.885" end="3:24.229">know</span> <span begin="3:24.229" end="3:24.560">who</span> <span begin="3:24.560" end="3:24.917">we</span> <span begin="3:24.917" end="3:25.549">are)</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">你清楚我们的身份</span></span></p><p begin="3:25.593" end="3:28.979" itunes:key="L57" ttm:agent="v1"><span begin="3:25.593" end="3:25.900">We&apos;re</span> <span begin="3:25.900" end="3:26.173">the</span> <span begin="3:26.173" end="3:26.555">ones</span> <span begin="3:26.555" end="3:26.853">with</span> <span begin="3:26.853" end="3:27.468">matching</span> <span begin="3:27.468" end="3:28.979">scars</span><span ttm:role="x-translation" xml:lang="zh-Hans">正是与你共有相似伤疤的人</span></p></div></body></tt>